225800000X	225800000X	Respiratory, Developmental, Rehabilitative and Restorative Service Providers	Recreation Therapist	\N	A recreation therapist uses recreational activities for intervention in some physical, social or emotional behavior to bring about a desired change in that behavior and promote the growth and development of the patient.	Source: Joel A. DeLisa and Bruce M. Gans, Rehabilitation Medicine: Principles and Practice Second Edition, J.B. Lippincott Company, Philadelphia: 1993, p. 7	\N	\N	\N	metaTaxonomyCode:225800000X	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f
